data.description: Incredible Investment Opportunity! Must-See 2-Unit Gem! This remarkable property is a testament to modern comfort and style, offering an amazing opportunity for both investors and homeowners. Prepare to be impressed by the recent renovations that have elevated this property to new heights. Enjoy the luxury of granite countertops, brand-new cabinets, stylish flooring, and energy-efficient windows.Each unit is equipped with convenient washer/dryer hookups, ensuring practicality and ease for the tenants.A touch of sophistication that sets this property apart are the luxurious bathrooms, featuring rejuvenating soaking tubs and separate walk-in showers.The property offers a 3bd/1ba unit and a 2bd/1ba - current tenants are on month-to-month leases, offering flexibility for either continued leasing or new ownership occupancy. Don't miss this great opportunity! Schedule your showing today!
